title: What if I am already enrolled in an associate degree program? - Quora

response.answer_text: This is an unfinished ask. So what? Complete what you started. Years later you will look back and will be glad that you did, besides, you will be able to model to your offspring and others that when it comes to education especially, you are a completer. Employers also like ppl who are completers, not only starters. Anybody can start something, it takes vision and commitment to complete a task that is worthwhile.
